      <h2>Best Virtual Credit Cards in India</h2>
      <p>Virtual credit cards represent the future of digital payments. These cards exist purely in digital form — with a unique card number, CVV, and expiry date stored securely in your banking app. They can be issued within seconds of approval, letting you start shopping online immediately without waiting 7-14 days for a physical card to arrive. Most banks now issue a virtual card alongside or before the physical card.</p>
      <p>Beyond convenience, virtual cards offer enhanced security for online shopping. You can generate one-time-use virtual card numbers, set spending limits per card, freeze and unfreeze instantly, and even create separate virtual cards for different merchants. If a virtual card number is compromised, you simply delete it and generate a new one — your primary account remains untouched.</p>

      <h2>Key Features of Virtual Credit Cards</h2>
      <ul class="feature-list">
        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Instant Activation:</strong> Get your virtual card number within 60 seconds of approval — start using immediately</li>
        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Enhanced Online Security:</strong> Generate unique card numbers for each merchant to prevent data breach exposure</li>
        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Contactless Payments:</strong> Add to Google Pay, Apple Pay, or Samsung Pay for tap-to-pay at physical stores</li>
        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Instant Card Controls:</strong> Freeze, unfreeze, set limits, and manage your card in real-time from your app</li>
        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>UPI Integration:</strong> Link your virtual credit card to UPI apps for scan-and-pay at any QR code merchant</li>
        <li><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> <strong>Physical Card Optional:</strong> Use the virtual card permanently or request a physical card when needed</li>
      </ul>

